text: Bob Lutz or Robert Lutz may refer to: *Bob Lutz (American football) (active 1969-2012), American high school football coach *Bobby Lutz (basketball) (born 1958), American college basketball coach *Bob Lutz (businessman) (born 1932), retired auto industry executive *Bob Lutz (tennis) (born 1947), American tennis player of the 1970s == See also == *Lutz
title: Bob Lutz
